        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4246",
        "content": "Tradition says: \"A trapper named Scott, while returning to the States, was robbed and stripped by the Indians.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4246_12544_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4246/12544/4246_12544_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4246",
        "content": "He crawled to these Bluffs and there famished.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4246_12544_000033_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4246/12544/4246_12544_000033_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4246",
        "content": "This occurred prior to eighteen thirty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4246_12544_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4246/12544/4246_12544_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4246",
        "content": "The tire bore this simple inscription: \"Rebecca Winters, aged fifty years.\" The hoofs of stock tramped the sunken grave and trod it into dust, but the arch of the tire remained to defy the strength of thoughtless hands that would have removed it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
